    "# Lassa Fever Data Cleaner & Validator\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook cleans and validates the scraped NCDC data, handles missing values, detects outliers, and creates analysis-ready datasets for the Lassa fever outbreak monitoring system.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Table of Contents\n",
    "1. [Setup & Data Loading](#setup)\n",
    "2. [Data Quality Assessment](#quality)\n",
    "3. [Data Cleaning](#cleaning)\n",
    "4. [Missing Value Imputation](#imputation)\n",
    "5. [Outlier Detection & Treatment](#outliers)\n",
    "6. [Data Validation](#validation)\n",
    "7. [Export Clean Data](#export)\n",
    "8. [Summary Statistics](#summary)"
   ]
  },
